{"tid":950433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關鍵報告：美國人近20年來變得越胖及越矮","createTime":"2018-12-21T13:41:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-21T16:02:46.000Z","uid":212399,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9484055d63e2ffc0ee408ef5978f04f91914d045","tid":950433,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T13:41:48.000Z","msg":"國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n美國「國家衞生統計中心」(National Center for Health Statistics)周四(20日)發表報告指出：美國人在過去近20年內變得越來越胖及越矮。<br />\n統計顯示，全美有40%的人被視為有肥胖問題，為醫療帶來巨大負擔，連帶也會影響經濟。<br />\n報告指出，1999年時，男性的平均體重為86公斤， 但在2015至2016年的最新數字裡，平均體重已增加至89.8公斤。 女性的體重也從1999年的74公斤，上升到2015至2016年時77公斤。<br />\n此外，男性腰圍由99公分增加至102公分；女性腰圍則由92公分增加至至98公分。今天美國男士平均身高為175.4公分，較1999年的 175.6公分稍矮。<br />\n男性身體質量指數(BMI)由27.8增至29.1；女性BMI則由27.8升至28.2，可見男女的肥胖問題正在上升。 不過，這份報告並未就上述趨勢提出解釋。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20181221/1336845.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20181221%2F1336845.htm&d=Hr6YcpbB53ZKSqCYDQqOFAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=f6939d6c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20181221/1336845.htm</a>"},{"pid":"008a7be9091a7d1edc622e8e8eaebf3f975aa227","tid":950433,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T13:43:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87afee9c77aa2c0fa0cb9fbc98bcad4feed4d55f","tid":950433,"uid":213441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T13:44:52.000Z","msg":"我地中國人食蒙牛 越飲越高大<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44c853200ab45ebfbcc54490c1bb108ee46db534","tid":950433,"uid":41356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T14:41:55.000Z","msg":"平均差唔多90kg<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe3ff5db05e72979081b2a87dd8743b84502612d","tid":950433,"uid":49197,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T14:44:27.000Z","msg":"175.6&gt;175.4咁唔明顯都夾硬分析<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，降得果0.114%"},{"pid":"eaf1f00991f2481420910039f37598be18d295c2","tid":950433,"uid":121546,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T15:34:42.000Z","msg":"矮左係因為非白人人種多左<br />\n肥就真係因為美國人肥左"},{"pid":"3415cd10712812d36c709009cd4f6168eed86ec6","tid":950433,"uid":80072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T16:00:31.000Z","msg":"老老實實第一次去洛杉磯嗰陣覺得啲人冇想像咁高"},{"pid":"c9c3a47dd0ea671e7d40ae769b5632bd0eaf39cc","tid":950433,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe3ff5db05e72979081b2a87dd8743b84502612d","tid":950433,"uid":49197,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T14:44:27.000Z","msg":"175.6&gt;175.4咁唔明顯都夾硬分析<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，降得果0.114%"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T16:02:46.000Z","msg":"夾硬黎<br />\n<br />\n咁小%, 其實隨時都唔奇"}]}